  <summary date="2022-03-07T22:30:37Z" status="Introduced in House">Safe School Drinking Water Act

This bill requires the Environmental Protection Agency to establish a program to award grants to assist local educational agencies in installing and maintaining filtration stations (e.g., drinking fountains) at schools and child care programs.</summary>
